title: Deon Cole: A Joke about Livin' It Up
description: Deon Cole jokes about livin' it up in his Netflix special, "Cole Hearted". Grab your tickets at NetflixIsAJokeFest.com to see Deon and your other favorite comedians in the Netflix is a Joke Fest happening April 28th-May 8th in Los Angeles.
